(4, 4, 79, '第十三届全国战斗部与毁伤技术学术交流会成功举办', '<P><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 由中国宇航学会无人飞行器分会战斗部与毁伤技术专业委员会、爆炸科学与技术国家重点实验室（北京理工大学）主办的第十三届全国战斗部与毁伤技术学术交流会于9月21日~23日在安徽黄山市举行。战斗部与毁伤技术专业委员会主任委员、北京理工大学冯顺山教授主持了学术大会，爆炸科学与技术国家重点实验室副主任王成教授、兵器工业第203所副所长李立群研究员分别代表主办和承办单位致辞。来自北京理工大学、南京理工大学、中北大学、北京科技大学、国防科技大学、二炮工程学院、海军航空工程学院等高校，中国工程物理研究院、航空、航天、兵器、船舶系统的研究所及企业，炮兵装备技术研究所、空军装备研究院总体所、第三军医大学、工程兵科研三所、跟踪与通信技术研究所军内单位共55个单位的229名代表参加了本次学术交流会。</FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<IMG style="WIDTH: 428px; HEIGHT: 288px" src="/labadmin/uploadfile/201310081381191336.jpg" width=383 height=213></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">专业委员会主任委员冯顺山教授主持学术大会</SPAN></B></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <IMG style="WIDTH: 428px; HEIGHT: 277px" src="/labadmin/uploadfile/201310081381191400.jpg" width=423 height=199></SPAN></B></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">爆炸科学与技术国家重点实验室副主任王成教授致辞</SPAN></B> </FONT></SPAN></B></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </STRONG><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 16px">中国北方科技信息研究所郭美芳研究员、第三军医大学王正国院士、兵器工业204所肖川研究员、炮研所孙韬高工等11名特邀专家分别作了题为“国外弹药高效毁伤技术的发展”、“新型人员易损性评估模型及其在毁伤评估中的应用”、“火炸药及高能毁伤技术的发展”、“破片杀伤战斗部及毁伤技术的发展”的特邀报告，另外12名代表作了大会报告，32名代表在2个分组会场作了报告。</FONT></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <IMG style="WIDTH: 435px; HEIGHT: 288px" src="/labadmin/uploadfile/201310081381191525.jpg" width=436 height=193></FONT></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">大会主会场报告</FONT></SPAN></B></FONT></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT size=3><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <IMG style="WIDTH: 435px; HEIGHT: 294px" src="/labadmin/uploadfile/201310081381191581.jpg" width=436 height=193></SPAN></B></FONT></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT size=3><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">大会分会场报告</FONT></SPAN></B></SPAN></B></FONT></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </STRONG><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 16px">本届学术交流会呈现出以下特点：1.论文数量多、质量高、覆盖范围广；会议论文集3册共收录论文299篇，创下历届之最，体现了行业内科技工作者近2年来在毁伤技术、目标易损性、战斗部机理、终点弹道、毁伤效率、火炸药应用等方面的理论、数值模拟、试验技术和工程应用方面的研究成果，其中68篇论文被收入《弹箭与制导学报》增刊； 2.学术交流互动性好，台下代表们积极思考并提问发言，与报告人形成了极佳的互动氛围；3.参会和进行学术报告的年轻科技工作者多，预示着本领域蓬勃发展、后继有人。与会代表一致认为通过本次交流会开阔了视野，启发了思路，达到了“交流、开放、互动、启示”的目的，专业委员会为跨单位、跨领域学术交流提供了纽带与桥梁，对本专业领域的发展起到了的促进作用。</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px" size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <IMG style="WIDTH: 423px; HEIGHT: 290px" src="/labadmin/uploadfile/201310081381191729.jpg" width=443 height=183> </FON