AN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">20</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes">11</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">年</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes">9</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">月<FONT face="Times New Roman">2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes">0</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">—2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes">3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">日</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">中国&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;南京</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">“国际推进剂、炸药、烟火技术秋季</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">研</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">讨会”，每两年在我国召开一次，已成功地举办了</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">8</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">届，分别是</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">1996</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">年（北京）、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">1997</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">年（深圳）、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">1999</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">年（成都）、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">2001</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">年（绍兴）、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">2003</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">年（桂林）、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">2005</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">年（北京）、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">2007</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">年（西安）和</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">2009</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">年（昆明）。会议</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">在美国、俄罗斯、德国、英国、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">加拿大、意大利、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">日本、以色列、波兰等十多个国家中得到积极响应，同时也得到了国内有关单位、部门的大力支持和踊跃参与。会议论文集论文被EI、ISTP及CA等国际知名检索机构收录。基于该会议的广泛影响和传统，我们拟</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">于</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">20</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">11</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">年</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">9</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">月2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">0</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">—2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">日在</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">南京</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">举办&nbsp;“20</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">11</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">国际推进剂、炸药、烟火技术秋季</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">研</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">讨会”，现征集会议论文，有关</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">事项</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">如下。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 15.6pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">共同主办单位</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">中国兵工学会</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">北京理工大学</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">湖北航天化学技术研究所</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: