/SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">20</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">11</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">年</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">月<FONT face="Times New Roman">20</FONT><FONT face=宋体>日前提供论文全文</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">。另页</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">附中文题名、作者、单位、摘要、关键词及联系人、联系方式（电话、<FONT face="Times New Roman">E-mail</FONT><FONT face=宋体>、通信地址）。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 15.6pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">会议费用</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">为了保证会议质量和参会人员的权益，在论文录用后每篇论文须一次性交纳</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">21</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">00<FONT face=宋体>元人民币（限</FONT><FONT face="Times New Roman">6</FONT><FONT face=宋体>页之内，超过</FONT><FONT face="Times New Roman">6</FONT><FONT face=宋体>页的，每页再加</FONT><FONT face="Times New Roman">200</FONT><FONT face=宋体>元），不论是否参加会议都要交纳。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">此</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">费用包括：论文版面费、一位作者</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">的</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">会议注册费和会议论文集一套。住宿费用自理。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">论文作者</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">不能参加会议的，其他人</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">不能代替</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">非论文作者参会需交纳<FONT face="Times New Roman">1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">00<FONT face=宋体>元会议注册费，论文集需另购买。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">对于<FONT face="Times New Roman">1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">篇论文</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">作者中参会人员多于<FONT face="Times New Roman">1</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人的，需</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">交纳会议注册费</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 15.6pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">会议展览</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">会议期间欢迎相关单位展示科研成果、新产品、新技术。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 15.6pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">会议筹备秘书处</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p19 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">联系人：李生才副教授</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;郭新亚老师</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p19 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 48pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">陈</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">朗教授</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">冯长根教授</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">地</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">址：北京市海淀区中关村南大街</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">号</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p16 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 35.91pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">北京理工大学安全与环境学报杂志社</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">邮</SPAN><SP