-TOP: #000000 0.5pt solid; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle; BORDER-LEFT: #000000 0.5pt solid; WIDTH: 54pt; COLOR: #000000; BORDER-BOTTOM: #000000 0.5pt solid; FONT-STYLE: normal; WHITE-SPACE: normal; HEIGHT: 24.75pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-protection: locked visible" width=72 height=33 x:num="30">\r\n<P align=center>30</P></TD>\r\n<TD class=et2 style="BORDER-RIGHT: #000000 0.5pt solid; BORDER-TOP: #000000 0.5pt solid; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle; BORDER-LEFT: #000000 0.5pt solid; WIDTH: 75.75pt; COLOR: #000000; BORDER-BOTTOM: #000000 0.5pt solid; FONT-STYLE: normal; WHITE-SPACE: normal; HEIGHT: 24.75pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-protection: locked visible" width=101 height=33>\r\n<P align=center>&nbsp;</P></TD>\r\n<TD class=et2 style="BORDER-RIGHT: #000000 0.5pt solid; BORDER-TOP: #000000 0.5pt solid; FONT-WEIGHT: 400; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle; BORDER-LEFT: #000000 0.5pt solid; WIDTH: 246.75pt; COLOR: #000000; BORDER-BOTTOM: #000000 0.5pt solid; FONT-STYLE: normal; WHITE-SPACE: normal; HEIGHT: 24.75pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-protection: locked visible" width=329 height=33>\r\n<P align=center>&nbsp;</P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></P>', '2010-12-07', 1399989402, 'wangte');
INSERT INTO `np_article` (`aid`, `ord`, `type`, `title`, `content`, `add_date`, `add_time`, `add_user`) VALUES
(311, 311, 75, '中国力学学会青年学术沙龙第58次活动通知', '<DIV class=Section0 style="LAYOUT-GRID:  15.6pt none">\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 中国力学学会青年学术沙龙第<FONT face="Times New Roman">58</FONT><FONT face=宋体>次活动定于</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-spacerun: yes">20</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">10<FONT face=宋体>年</FONT><FONT face="Times New Roman">11</FONT><FONT face=宋体>月</FONT><FONT face="Times New Roman">23</FONT><FONT face=宋体>日（星期二）下午</FONT><FONT face="Times New Roman">15:00</FONT><FONT face=宋体>在</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">北京理工大学</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">国际教育交流中心举行。本次活动由中国力学学会主办，北京理工大学承办。现将相关事宜通知如下：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 120%"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 120%"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">一、时间地点</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">时间：&nbsp;20</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">10年11月23日（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">星期二</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">）15:00</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">地点：&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">北京理工大学国际教育交流中心三层第一会议室</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">乘车路线：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">自驾车或乘出租车由北三环东向西行驶，从长春桥路/苏州街/魏公村出口进辅路，在苏州桥掉头，进入北京理工大学北门即是。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">联系人：张庆明&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;电话：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">13701167122</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;王丽琼&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;电话：13910393993</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 120%"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">二、会议安排</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">1.&nbsp;<FONT face=宋体>开幕报告：爆炸科学与技术国家重点实验室力学及相关学科的建设与发展</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">报告人：张庆明教授（北京理工大学爆炸科学与技术国家重点实验室主任）</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">2.&nbsp;<FONT face=宋体>主题报告：基于多尺度分析的点火——反应起爆研究</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">报告人：黄风雷教授（北京理工大学机械与运载学部主任）</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">3.&nbsp;<FONT face=宋体>专题报告：高超声速研究进展</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">报告人：中国科学院力学研究所</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">4.&nbsp;<FONT face=宋体>联谊活动：</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">保龄球、卡拉<FONT face="Times New Roman">OK</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">沙龙活动提供晚餐</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 120%"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">三、回执：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 21pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">为了更好地组织与安排此次活动，请您于<FONT face="Times New Roman">2010</FONT><FONT face=宋体>年</FONT><FONT face="Times New Roman">11</FONT><FONT face=宋体>月</FONT><FONT face="Times New Roman">15</FONT><FONT face=宋体>日前将以下回执反馈到</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">中国力学学会办公室郭亮处。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">电子邮箱：</SPAN><SPAN><A href="mailto:guoliang@cstam.org.cn"><SPAN class=15 style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,255); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; TEXT-DECORATION: underline; mso-spacerun: yes">guoliang@cstam.org.cn</SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;电话：&nbsp;13810171862</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-spacerun: yes"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<TABLE style="PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; mso-table-layout-alt: fixed" align=center>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR style="HEIGHT: 32.7pt">\r\n<TD style="BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; WIDTH: 68.4pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.